dct_alternative_sm: Fort Walton Beach, bathymetric fishing map
Gulf of Mexico, Fort Walton Beach
dct_description_sm: Depths shown by isolines, soundings and gradient tints.
Includes hydrographic survey index and information, depth gradient diagram, and index to adjoining maps.
Also available via Internet from the NGDC NOAA web site. Address as of 2/11/08: http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/mgg/bathymetry/maps/previews/F-25.pdf; current access via PURL.
